graph LR
    TrainingOp[Training Operator]

    %% External Dependencies (Required for specific frameworks)
    TrainingOp -->|PyTorchJob runtime| PyTorch[PyTorch 1.x/2.x]
    TrainingOp -->|TFJob runtime| TensorFlow[TensorFlow 2.x]
    TrainingOp -->|JAXJob runtime| JAX[JAX Latest]
    TrainingOp -->|XGBoostJob runtime| XGBoost[XGBoost 1.x+]
    TrainingOp -->|PaddleJob runtime| PaddlePaddle[PaddlePaddle 2.x]
    TrainingOp -->|MPIJob runtime| MPI[OpenMPI / Intel MPI]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional)
    TrainingOp -.->|gang scheduling| Volcano[Volcano 1.x+]
    TrainingOp -.->|job queueing| Kueue[Kueue 0.5+]

    %% Platform Dependencies
    TrainingOp -->|orchestration| K8s[Kubernetes API]
    TrainingOp -->|container images| Registry[Container Registry]
    TrainingOp -->|certificates| CertManager[cert-manager]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    TrainingOp -->|model registration| ModelRegistry[Model Registry]
    TrainingOp -->|data/checkpoints| S3[S3 Storage]
    TrainingOp -->|experiment tracking| MLFlow[MLFlow]

    %% Integration Points (ODH Components that use Training Operator)
    Notebooks[Notebooks / Workbenches] -->|submit jobs| TrainingOp
    Pipelines[Data Science Pipelines] -->|pipeline steps| TrainingOp
    Ray[Ray] -.->|hybrid workloads| TrainingOp

    %% External Services
    TrainingOp -->|package installation| PyPI[PyPI / pip index]

    %% Styling
    style TrainingOp fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:4px,color:#fff

    style PyTorch fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style TensorFlow fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style JAX fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style XGBoost fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style PaddlePaddle fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style MPI fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style Volcano fill:#ccc,stroke:#333,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style Kueue fill:#ccc,stroke:#333,stroke-dasharray: 5 5

    style K8s fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333
    style Registry fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333
    style CertManager fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333
    style PyPI fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333

    style ModelRegistry fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style S3 fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style MLFlow fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style Notebooks fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style Pipelines fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style Ray fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333

    %% Legend
    subgraph Legend
        Req[Required Runtime<br/>External]
        Opt[Optional<br/>External]
        Platform[Platform Service]
        ODH[Internal ODH]
    end

    style Req fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style Opt fill:#ccc,stroke:#333,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style Platform fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333
    style ODH fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
